 Zella Jackson Price , 76 , and Melanie Diane Gilmore , 49 , met in-person at Price 's Olivette home .
When Price gave birth at Homer G. Phillips Hospital , she was told shortly after delivery that the infant had died .
But the baby was alive and for an unknown reason been given up for adoption .
Price and Gilmore embraced when she was still told by doctors her baby , which was prematurely born , died .